-- Bank of Korea’s Kim Urges Closer Attention to Price Goal in ‘12
-- B y   E u n k y u n g   S e o
-- 2011-12-30T06:00:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-30/bank-of-korea-s-kim-urges-closer-attention-to-price-goal-in-12.html
The  Bank of Korea  should pay closer
attention to achieving its inflation target in 2012, Governor
Kim Choong Soo said in a New Year speech released today. While
supply-side inflation pressures are likely to weaken,
expectations for prices to rise remain “high,” Kim said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eunkyung Seo in Seoul at 
